w/cpp/numeric/math/round) in c++11.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I believe the dependency on boost/random.hpp can be elminated with <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/C++11#Extensible_random_number_facility\" rel=\"nofollow\">c++11 random number improvements</a>. The other dependency is boost::math::round, and I believe this is now <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/numeric/math/round\" rel=\"nofollow\">std::round</a> in c++11.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2014-04-07T16:58:00.837848+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2014-04-09T18:48:16.725531+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 2}